summary: LETTER TO CONGRESSMAN CASS BALENGER CONCERNING  MR JIM EUREY'S  OPPOSITION TO THOS EPROVISIONS OF EARLY WARNING REPORT (EWR) REGULATIONS THAT REQUIRE MANUFACTURERS THAT PRODUCE OVER 500 SMALL-TO-MEDIUM TRAILERS (THOSE WITH A GROSS WEIGHT RATING, GVWR,    OF UNDER 26000 POUNDS) TO ISSUE A COMPREHENSIVE EARLY WARNING REPORT TO NHTSA. SUCJ REPORT, ACCORDING TO MR, EUREY WOULD PUT HIM AND SOME OF HIS COLLEAGUES IN TRAILERS OUT OF BUSINESS.  *JB...*AK
